ist" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MadScientist">Hououin Kyouma</a>.</li></ul></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/IDidntTellYouBecauseYoudBeUnhappy" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/IDidntTellYouBecauseYoudBeUnhappy">I Didn't Tell You Because You'd Be Unhappy</a>: There is <em>no</em> good way to tell your best friend that <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile"> they're going to die within hours and you've personally witnessed it <em>countless</em> times in your attempts to prevent it</span>. So Okabe doesn't.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/IfItsYouItsOkay" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/IfItsYouItsOkay">If It's You, It's Okay</a>: As far as Daru is concerned, Luka's just as ripe for <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/YuriFan" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/YuriFan">Yuri Fan</a> fantasies as any of his other non-Okabe friends, actual sex be damned.<div class="indent"><strong>Daru:</strong> It's gettin' pretty yuri in there. <br><strong>Okabe:</strong> Lukako's a guy. <br><strong>Daru:</strong> That makes it even <em>better</em>.</div></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TheIlluminati" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TheIlluminati">The Illuminati</a>: The group pulling SERN's strings. They are only obliquely referred to as "The Committee of 300" and nothing is ever revealed about them. However, <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VisualNovel/ChaosHead" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VisualNovel/ChaosHead">you learn more</a> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VisualNovel/RoboticsNotes" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VisualNovel/RoboticsNotes">about them</a> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VisualNovel/ChaosChild" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VisualNovel/ChaosChild">in the other Science Adventure entries...</a></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ImHavingSoulPains" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.p